-# locals: (events:)

- return if events.blank?

%details.card
  %summary.fw-semibold Manual seasonal attendance update
  %p.mt-3 Use this fallback if the automatic weekly update misses a seasonal.
  %p
    Marks the kids who attended that event as having attended a seasonal event,
    so they don't get the first seasonal discount.
  .d-flex.justify-content-center.flex-wrap.gap-3
    - events.each do |event_name|
      = button_to event_name,
                  attended_seasonal_path(event_name:),
                  class: 'btn btn-primary',
                  method: :patch
